org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.java.reverse.javaparser.ast

Class TypeParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.java.reverse.javaparser.ast.Node
      • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.java.reverse.javaparser.ast.TypeParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, NamedNode

    public final class TypeParameter
extends Node
implements NamedNode

    This class represents the declaration of a generics argument.

    The TypeParameter is constructed following the syntax:
     
 TypeParameter ::= <IDENTIFIER> ( "extends" ClassOrInterfaceType ( "&" ClassOrInterfaceType )* )?
    Author:
    Julio Vilmar Gesser
